<p>Version&nbsp;<code>0.2.0</code>&nbsp;is a major step for the Whisper Engine &#8211;<br>introducing&nbsp;<strong>Category Pages</strong>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<strong>Post Sorting by Category</strong>.</p>



<span id="more-8067"></span>



<p><strong>What does this mean?</strong></p>



<p>Until now, posts lived in silence, scattered, hidden in the shadows of the feed.<br>Now, they gather under banners &#8211; clear, sharp, immutable.</p>



<p>Each category is its own cryptic channel:</p>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>Navigate only the content you want.</li>



<li>See the resistance by its divisions.</li>



<li>Control the flow of knowledge with precision.</li>
</ul>



<p><strong>Key Features:</strong></p>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li><strong>Category Index Pages</strong><br>Automatically generated pages list all posts tagged with that category, creating a clean, accessible map of your content.</li>



<li><strong>Sorting by Category</strong><br>Whisper Engine now sorts posts on index pages by their category, making navigation intuitive and deliberate.</li>



<li><strong>Lightweight &amp; Configurable</strong><br>No fluff.<br>No external dependencies.<br>Just silent efficiency.</li>
</ul>



<p>The Ghost does not shout.<br>It does not wander.<br>It moves with intent.</p>



